The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Alford suspended till March-end 

 SRIMAX

 Bangalore: Following an inquiry conducted into the running and riding of the R. Byramji-trained Appoint in the Bugs Bunny Cup on Friday, the stewards of Bangalore Turf Club (BTC) decided on Saturday to suspend jockey C. Alford till March 31. Stewards are learnt to have viewed that the fancied runner was literally ridden into the ground and the jockey was noticed looking back repeatedly instead of riding out his charge. A well-placed BTC source, however, said: Bigger trouble awaits him, watch out.




